{"title":"平凡伟大的书生——纪念吴玉章诞辰110周年","authors":["魏明伦"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"平凡伟大的书生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——纪念吴玉章诞辰110周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魏明伦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍茫大地路坎坷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志士仁人苦求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千名志士千重浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万缕英灵万丈波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一条川江激流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇入长江黄河；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一介平凡书生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自平凡村落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲不平世道砸枷锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建不凡业绩救中国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹉跎岁月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月蹉跎……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦回首——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨世纪沧桑变化多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事谁评说？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满头白发是见证——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见民主潮汐潮涨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证自由花开花落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少战果？多少苦果？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几代迂回？百年功过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回音壁前寻逝波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘陀路上再求索。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死求索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲歌慷慨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慷慨悲歌……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（编后附记：这是作者为电视连续剧《跨越世纪的悲歌》写的主题歌歌词）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}